1949;;Stop Press Girl;;British;;Michael Barry;;Sally Ann Howes, Gordon Jackson;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stop_Press_Girl;;Jennifer Peters is a normal girl except for one unfortunate trait. All the women in her family stop any mechanical contrivance that they travel in. As the film progresses, Jennifer stops her boyfriend's automobile, then a train she travels in without being aware of what she does. Tension mounts when a girlfriend takes ill and Jennifer takes her job; an air hostess on a Liberator airliner!